    {
      "id": "PopularPost162721",
      "post_content": "Look at the picture. This should be able to block any number of attackers. How about this:  \n  \n![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol)  \nWall of Sandstone  \n  \nCreature - Wall  \n  \nDefender  \nWall of Sanstone can block any number of creatures.  \nDamage to Wall of Sandstone is not erased at the end of turn.  \n  \n*It was enormous, but it still was only sand. - Okk*  \n  \n0/30  \n  \nOr this:  \n  \n![3](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=3&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol)![Red](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=R&type=symbol)  \nThe Great Wall of Anihc  \n  \nLegendary Creature - Wall  \n  \nDefender  \nShroud  \nThe Great Wall of Anich cannot block.  \nAt the end of attack phase all creatures that attacked you and were not blocked are buried if you control an untapped non-wall creature that wasn't blocking.  \n  \n*It didn't hinder advance, but blocked retreat. - Sun Zu*  \n  \n0/30",
      "posted_by": "tavaritz",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost162721\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Look at the picture. This should be able to block any number of attackers. How about this:<br/><br/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/><br/>Wall of Sandstone<br/><br/>Creature - Wall<br/><br/>Defender<br/>Wall of Sanstone can block any number of creatures.<br/>Damage to Wall of Sandstone is not erased at the end of turn.<br/><br/><i>It was enormous, but it still was only sand. - Okk</i><br/><br/>0/30<br/><br/>Or this:<br/><br/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"3\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=3&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/><img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Red\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=R&amp;type=symbol\"/><br/>The Great Wall of Anihc<br/><br/>Legendary Creature - Wall<br/><br/>Defender<br/>Shroud<br/>The Great Wall of Anich cannot block.<br/>At the end of attack phase all creatures that attacked you and were not blocked are buried if you control an untapped non-wall creature that wasn't blocking.<br/><br/><i>It didn't hinder advance, but blocked retreat. - Sun Zu</i><br/><br/>0/30</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '162721'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy58371\">tavaritz</span>\r\n                                (6/7/2011 12:01:43 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
