      "post_content": "@Tavaritz: I like that it's the great wall of China backwards. Problem is, that's more of a black ability (see [No Mercy](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=No Mercy) or [Dread](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Dread)).   \n  \nToday, they'd probably print Wall of Sandstone's ability by having it take damage in the form of -1/-1 counters (see [Phyrexian Hydra](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phyrexian Hydra)).",
